---
title: "VineMind AI — Recommendation Request Sequence Diagram"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Vineyard Manager
    participant FE as React Dashboard
    participant API as FastAPI REST API
    participant DE as Decision Intelligence<br/>Engine
    participant WSM as Water Stress<br/>Model
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>+ PostGIS

    User->>FE: Opens Dashboard
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/recommendations
    API->>DB: Query latest recommendations
    DB-->>API: Return recommendations list
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (recommendations)
    FE-->>User: Display priority list<br/>(Irrigate Immediately → No Action)

    User->>FE: Clicks on Block A
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/blocks/{blockA}
    API->>DB: Query block details + latest observation
    DB-->>API: Return block data
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (block details)
    FE-->>User: Display block overview<br/>(ETa, ETo, NDVI, Stress Score)

    User->>FE: Clicks "Why this recommendation?"
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/evidence/{blockA}
    API->>DB: Query Decision Evidence Package
    DB-->>API: Return DEP (stress_score,<br/>contributors, confidence, rules)
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (DEP)
    FE-->>User: Display explanation:<br/>"Irrigate Tonight — Stress Score 74/100<br/>Water deficit 4.2mm, declining NDVI,<br/>no rain forecast, veraison stage"

    User->>FE: Opens AI Copilot
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/copilot/chat
    Note over API: "Compare Block A and Block B"
    API->>DE: Retrieve DEPs for both blocks
    DE->>DB: Query observations + evidence
    DB-->>DE: Return data
    DE-->>API: Structured context
    API->>API: Build RAG context + LLM prompt
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (explanation)
    FE-->>User: "Block A (Score 74) needs attention<br/>before Block B (Score 45).<br/>Block A has higher water deficit<br/>and is at veraison..."

    User->>FE: Approves irrigation for Block A
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/recommendations/{id}/accept
    API->>DB: Update recommendation status
    DB-->>API: Confirmed
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (accepted)
    FE-->>User: "Irrigation approved for Block A"<br/>+ audit trail logged
